  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to Primary Education in Distant Areas of Helman (SPEDAH)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">First year of Support to Primary Education in Distant Areas of Helmand (SPEDAH) is part of ESPA I programme that supports implementation of National Education Strategic Plan through International Rescue Committee, a well reputed international organization in Afghanistan. The SPEDAH project responds to the key challenges of the lack of quality learning opportunities, the limited availability of suitable teachers, and the insufficient involvement of parents or caregivers in the education of their children. The project ultimate goal is for children and youth to have the knowledge and skills to be productive members of Afghan society.</narrative>
  </description>
